{"number":104,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍ","translation":"Woe to every scorner and mocker","transliteration":"Waylun likulli humazatin lumaza","page":601},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَالًا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","translation":"Who collects wealth and [continuously] counts it.","transliteration":"Allathee jamaAAa malanwaAAaddadah","page":601},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخْلَدَهُۥ","translation":"He thinks that his wealth will make him immortal.","transliteration":"Yahsabu anna malahu akhladah","page":601},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"كَلَّا ۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِى ٱلْحُطَمَةِ","translation":"No! He will surely be thrown into the Crusher.","transliteration":"Kalla layunbathanna fee alhutama","page":601},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْحُطَمَةُ","translation":"And what can make you know what is the Crusher?","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma alhutama","page":601},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمُوقَدَةُ","translation":"It is the fire of Allāh, [eternally] fueled,","transliteration":"Naru Allahi almooqada","page":601},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلْأَفْـِٔدَةِ","translation":"Which mounts directed at the hearts.","transliteration":"Allatee tattaliAAu AAalaal-af-ida","page":601},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيْهِم مُّؤْصَدَةٌ","translation":"Indeed, it [i.e., Hellfire] will be closed down upon them","transliteration":"lnnaha AAalayhim mu/sada","page":601},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"فِى عَمَدٍ مُّمَدَّدَةٍۭ","translation":"In extended columns.","transliteration":"Fee AAamadin mumaddada","page":601}]}